							h3(class="panel-title") So what is a gear?
						div(class="panel-body") A gear is one of a set of toothed wheels that work together to alter the relation between the speed of a driving mechanism and the speed of the driven parts. 
			div(class="row")
				div(class="col-md-12")
					div(class="panel panel-default")
